{"tid":523142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(外國) 男子跳樓壓死21個月大男童 兩人喪生","createTime":"2018-01-08T09:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T09:19:39.000Z","uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2242d41ec5ddd88d1e00b1932208e223cf04ac0","tid":523142,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭一名男童和家人剛結束慶祝新年，但男童不幸被一名跳樓輕生的男子壓中，重傷死亡。<br />\n<br />\n外電報導，這名男童才21個月大，當時一家與親友一起慶祝新年，結束之後，走出大廈，男童的母親和親友道別後，一瞬間發現兒子被一個人壓住，之後兩人都喪生。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，這名輕生的男子39歲，當時從8樓跳下。雖然救援員努力為男童急救，但最後不治。一名鄰居回憶起當時場面表示非常悲痛，男童母親的哭聲充滿悲哀，「我關上窗門，我不忍心再聽下去」。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示正在調查事件，釐清男子為何輕生，「調查他有沒有喝醉，或者有沒有其它原因令他這樣做」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBHRqeY.img?h=273&amp;w=270&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=254&amp;y=213\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBHRqeY.img%3Fh%3D273%26w%3D270%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D254%26y%3D213&h=da93a8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1fddc721d05e45795f789eae5fea325c1cbc6d","tid":523142,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"357064377760aefeb0b9eb5c83d3c476acfbd7a2","tid":523142,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a89434e7e48fcb83f55b180af3d4f3b106a9737","tid":523142,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"生時累人，死時累街坊"},{"pid":"1e2ca9118c24650fab687ff5a8ac7c9fcc36ec08","tid":523142,"uid":139815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"仆街支那人累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}